race.comment: I AM THE TIGER (6) is a Strasbourg filly on debut for the Bain & Taylor partnership. Impressed in her recent trial win and is drawn favourably. Expecting her to hit the ground running. VERCELLI (8) returns and is another who has caught the eye in her lead-up work, looking to have progressed nicely. Draws to get the gun run for Tootell who sticks from jumpouts. Bold showing anticipated. DEBRALEE (3) can be excused for a flat run second-up from a 455-day break. Can improve sharply third-up and is worth keeping in mind. ASHREIGN (13) resumes. Has overall made a disappointing start but has shown glimpses of ability. Should be ready to go with a handful of hitouts in readiness.
